  <section class="tool-hero">
    <div class="tool-hero-inner">
      <div class="tool-badge"><span class="dot"></span>FREE TOOL // Channel Attribution</div>
      <h1>TikTok vs Meta <span class="green">ROAS Bridge</span> Calculator</h1>
      <p class="tool-hero-desc">Compare your actual TikTok and Meta performance after adjusting for attribution differences and tracking loss. Get a true blended ROAS and a data-driven budget split recommendation.</p>
      <div class="tool-trust">
